 REVISION HISTORY
================
------------------
2015-08-14
- packaging, add configure options

------------------
2015-08-03
- API changed(compression method argument is moved from fwrite() to fopen())
- change default encoder from normal to binary_search
- "normal" encoder is renamed to "original"
- support Zlib's compression level and strategy
- support LZ4 (optional)
- add build option to disable OpenMP
- add build option to disable Fortran Interface

------------------
2015-07-30
- introduce BUILD_DIR and update ug

------------------
2015-06-19
- introduce relative tolerance
- support variable write buffer for zlib
- support byte swap IO
- add fwrite() and fread() for signed/unsigned char, short, int and long

------------------
2014-12-31
- add copyright and contributors

------------------
2014-12-25
- create repository
